  <accessibilityDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Himalaia has adapted rooms available on request. The rooms have a wide bathroom door (approximetly 85cm) and hand rails access for the bath. </p>
<p>Although the has a central location,  the entrance for wheelchairs is via the underground parking ramp and staff lift.</p>
<p>Please give us a call to request an adapted room at this property, so we can ensure it is the right choice for you.</p>]]></accessibilityDescription>
