  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>Each day a continental breakfast buffet with additional hot options is served. </p>
<p>Enjoy a four course dinner from the buffet each day which includes a selection of soups, salads, mains and desserts from both the buffet and show kitchen. The dress code for meal service is smart-casual.</p>
<p>Christmas festive dinner is included on Christmas Eve and a New Year gala dinner and live music can be enjoyed at the New Year's Eve party.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
