  <description><![CDATA[<p>The comfortable and cosy Hotel Himalaia has a central location in <a data-udi="umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7bd0ea2aff2942389cbf8acdba0a0e77}" title="Soldeu">Soldeu</a>, so you are not far from the resort centre and gondola. After a day on the slopes there are some lovely leisure facilities available including a bar area with a pool table and a wellness area with a hot tub.</p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p>The Hotel Himalaia is a popular hotel with our Inghams guests, it is located in the centre of Soldeu, so all of the resort facilities are within easy reach. The main Soldeu gondola is accessible on foot in less than two minutes from the hotel. As the resort is a part of the vast Grandvalira ski region, you have access to more than 200 kilometres of slopes that range in level of difficulty, many of the runs are suitable for beginners and intermediates however there are some challenging runs for the more advanced skiers and boarders.</p>
<h2>Cosy and comfortable</h2>
<p>The charming rooms and studios are furnished in a contemporary style with inspiration coming from the Himalayas, and they offer an amazing value in addition to all of the modern comforts that are required to make you feel like you are at home.</p>
<h2>Relax and unwind</h2>
<p>The hotel has a cosy bar which features a pool table, a games area, and an internet corner, which are available to use while you are not out on the mountain or exploring Soldeu.</p>
<p>Visit the wellness area to give your sore muscles some much-needed relief, which includes a hot tub, steam room, and sauna. If relaxing isn't your thing, you can always take advantage of the workout area, which has a number of different machines and equipment to choose from. There is a local charge to use the wellness and fitness facilities,  you just need to book your time slot with the reception.</p>]]></description>
