  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Located in the centre of Soldeu close to the gondola, the Tibetan-themed reception and lounge areas provide a warm welcoming atmosphere and many Inghams guests return year after year to this popular hotel. The tasteful rooms and studios offer excellent value with modern comforts, and you'll have breakfast and dinner included as this hotel is offered on a half board basis. </p>]]></listingDescription>
