  <locationDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Excellent location in the centre of Soldeu</li>
<li>75 metres to the main ski gondola with the ski school meeting place at the top of the gondola</li>
<li>Ski hire shop is just next door</li>
<li>There is a public bus for Pas de la Casa, El Tarter and Andorra La Vella with a bus stop just 20 metres from the hotel</li>
<li>Soldeu has a medical centre, pharmacy, ATM and supermarket, all within a few minutes' walk from the hotel</li>
<li>The nearest pool is at the Hotel Hermitage (5 minutes' walk) or the Caldea Spa in Andorra la Vella (45 minutes by bus). Entrance charges apply. </li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></locationDescription>
