  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin/ Double Rooms</strong> are 25m² and can sleep between two to three people. Twin or double beds are available and some of these rooms have a sofa bed for the third person.</p>
<p>The Twin/ Double rooms are also available on request for sole occupancy, please call us to book this room type.</p>
<p><strong>Studios</strong> are 29m² and can sleep between two to three people. Studios are slightly bigger with two single beds and a sofa bed.</p>
<p><strong>One bedroom apartments </strong>are 37m² and can sleep between three to four people. The apartments contain a twin bedroom and a lounge area with two single sofa beds, which are best suited for children. </p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>All have a bath with shower head attachments and WC</li>
<li>Studios and apartments have a kitchenette with microwave and fridge</li>
<li>Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Satellite TV</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Room Safe</li>
<li>Telephone</li>
<li>Minibar/mini fridge </li>
<li>All rooms are non-smoking</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
